fields.title: The social network
fields.review: Arguably the best film of 21st century. Aaron Sorkin's razor sharp dialogues juggling around two at times three timelines and absolutely brilliant direction by David Fincher makes this billionaire drama worth a watch.

fields.title: Fast and Furious 6
fields.review: Great movie all in all very entertaining and drama like gets you on the edge of your seat as well as the other fast and furious . It’s tho truly incredible movie. It’s worth your time!

fields.title: Spiderman no way home
fields.review: Absolutely loved this movie I will say the first half hour felt kinda slow and took a bit to get the ball rolling but once it did IT NEVER STOPPED! Action was consistent and great

fields.title: Thor love and Thunder
fields.review: funny, romantic, and amazing superhero film that welcomes newcomers to the MCU

fields.title: Guardians of the Galaxy
fields.review: Great movie, it has a great storyline with some plotholes but nothing that can't be overlooked

fields.title: Aquaman
fields.review: GOOD MOVIE! DC comics have done quiet a good job with this movie unlike their recent projects(except Wonderwomen) which for some reasons didn't do that good.

fields.title: Top Gun - maverick
fields.review: Great Movie there was a fantastic balance of dominating and quiet personalities, big egos and humility, hotshots and not-so-confident pilots, and hotties and geeks. Nothing was overdone, not even the humor or drama

fields.title: Parasite
fields.review: I had no expectations walking into Parasite, but now my love and appreciation for it has breached the stratosphere. This is definitely one of the best movies of 2019, and it's bound to be a classic.

fields.title: Pokémon Detective Pikachu
fields.review: A fun loving movie that can still be understood by those who aren't avid Pokémon fans if you were thinking otherwise

fields.title: Suicide Squad
fields.review: An absolute blast! I had so much fun with this movie. There are so many things I loved about this movie.
